summary:
I spent some time trying to recreate a Nord version of world famous chef Gordon Ramsay. I did it for kicks, but who knows... Some one out there may just be dreaming of chefing up Skyrim as Gordon Ramsay. If that is you, then I bestow this gift upon thee.

When the construction set comes out I\'ll see about upgrading.
